flowchart LR
  %% DAW Architecture - Operation-Based Collaboration Model

  User[User]

  subgraph Client["Browser / Engine Layer"]
    direction TB
    UI["React UI / Track Viewer"]
    VisualRenderer["Visual Project Renderer"]
    AudioEditingEngine["Audio Editing Engine"]
    PlaybackEngine["Playback Engine / Web Audio"]
    PluginHost["Plugin Host\nWeb Audio Plugin Graph"]
    PluginDefinitionCache["Plugin Definition Cache"]
    IngestEngine["Ingest Engine"]
    ProjectSyncEngine["Project Sync Engine"]
    LocalOperationQueue["Local Operation Queue"]
    OperationReducer["Operation Reducer\nProject State Reducer"]
    LocalProjectState["Local Project State"]
    IndexedDB["IndexedDB / Local Cache"]
    WaveformCache["Waveform Peaks Cache"]
  end

  subgraph Server["Server Layer"]
    direction TB
    Auth["Auth / Permissions"]
    CommandAPI["Command API / Bootstrap API"]
    RealtimeGateway["Realtime Gateway\nops • presence • transport • asset-status"]
    PresenceService["Presence Service"]
    AssetAPI["Asset API / Signed URLs"]
    PluginRegistryAPI["Plugin Registry API"]
    SnapshotBuilder["Snapshot Builder"]
  end

  subgraph Persistence["Persistence"]
    direction TB
    ProjectOperationLog[(Project Operation Log)]
    ProjectSnapshots[(Project Snapshots)]
    AudioAssetMetadata[(AudioAsset Metadata)]
    PluginMetadata[(PluginDefinition / PluginPreset Metadata)]
    ObjectStorage[(Object Storage\nRaw Audio + Waveform Peaks)]
  end

  User --> UI

  UI --> AudioEditingEngine
  UI --> PlaybackEngine
  UI --> PluginHost
  UI --> IngestEngine
  UI --> VisualRenderer

  AudioEditingEngine -->|optimistic operations| LocalOperationQueue
  LocalOperationQueue -->|local apply| OperationReducer
  LocalOperationQueue -->|ordered edits / retries / dedupe| ProjectSyncEngine

  ProjectSyncEngine -->|bootstrap / send committed ops| CommandAPI
  CommandAPI --> Auth
  CommandAPI --> ProjectOperationLog
  ProjectOperationLog --> SnapshotBuilder
  SnapshotBuilder --> ProjectSnapshots
  ProjectSnapshots -->|latest snapshot| CommandAPI
  ProjectOperationLog -->|op tail after snapshot| CommandAPI

  CommandAPI -->|accepted committed ops| RealtimeGateway
  RealtimeGateway -->|remote accepted ops| ProjectSyncEngine
  ProjectSyncEngine -->|remote ops| OperationReducer
  OperationReducer --> LocalProjectState

  ProjectSyncEngine -->|send presence / transport| RealtimeGateway
  RealtimeGateway --> PresenceService
  PresenceService --> RealtimeGateway
  RealtimeGateway -->|remote presence / transport| ProjectSyncEngine

  ProjectSyncEngine -->|cache bootstrap + accepted ops| IndexedDB
  IndexedDB -->|restore cached project| ProjectSyncEngine

  LocalProjectState -->|render tree| VisualRenderer
  VisualRenderer --> UI

  PlaybackEngine -->|reads tracks / regions / transport state| LocalProjectState
  PluginHost -->|reads plugin chains| LocalProjectState
  PluginHost -->|reads plugin definitions| PluginDefinitionCache
  PluginHost -->|builds local Web Audio graph| PlaybackEngine

  ProjectSyncEngine -->|fetch plugin definitions / presets| PluginRegistryAPI
  PluginRegistryAPI --> Auth
  PluginRegistryAPI --> PluginMetadata
  PluginMetadata --> PluginRegistryAPI
  PluginRegistryAPI --> PluginDefinitionCache

  IngestEngine -->|generate peaks locally| WaveformCache
  IngestEngine -->|request signed upload| AssetAPI
  AssetAPI --> Auth
  AssetAPI --> ObjectStorage
  AssetAPI --> AudioAssetMetadata
  AssetAPI -->|emit ASSET_ADDED op| CommandAPI

  ObjectStorage -->|signed audio / peaks download| IngestEngine
  AudioAssetMetadata --> AssetAPI